_should_start_disabled

private boolean _should_start_disabled
Indicates whether tab of this modul should be disabled at the start of the application or not. Its set on true if setEnabled() method is invoked in implementation of load method. Load method is invoked by core before assigning tab to modul. Core ask modul at the beginning wheter it should disable the modul at the beginning.
